o-level-number-position:left;\\n\\ttext-indent:-.25in;\\n\\tfont-family:Symbol;}\\n@list l0:level5\\n\\t{mso-level-number-format:bullet;\\n\\tmso-level-text:o;\\n\\tmso-level-tab-stop:none;\\n\\tmso-level-number-position:left;\\n\\ttext-indent:-.25in;\\n\\tfont-family:\\\"Courier New\\\";}\\n@list l0:level6\\n\\t{mso-level-number-format:bullet;\\n\\tmso-level-text:\\uf0a7;\\n\\tmso-level-tab-stop:none;\\n\\tmso-level-number-position:left;\\n\\ttext-indent:-.25in;\\n\\tfont-family:Wingdings;}\\n@list l0:level7\\n\\t{mso-level-number-format:bullet;\\n\\tmso-level-text:\\uf0b7;\\n\\tmso-level-tab-stop:none;\\n\\tmso-level-number-position:left;\\n\\ttext-indent:-.25in;\\n\\tfont-family:Symbol;}\\n@list l0:level8\\n\\t{mso-level-number-format:bullet;\\n\\tmso-level-text:o;\\n\\tmso-level-tab-stop:none;\\n\\tmso-level-number-position:left;\\n\\ttext-indent:-.25in;\\n\\tfont-family:\\\"Courier New\\\";}\\n@list l0:level9\\n\\t{mso-level-number-format:bullet;\\n\\tmso-level-text:\\uf0a7;\\n\\tmso-level-tab-stop:none;\\n\\tmso-level-number-position:left;\\n\\ttext-indent:-.25in;\\n\\tfont-family:Wingdings;}\\nol\\n\\t{margin-bottom:0in;}\\nul\\n\\t{margin-bottom:0in;}\\n-->\\n<\\/style>\\n<!--[if gte mso 10]>\\n<style>\\n \\/* Style Definitions *\\/\\n table.MsoNormalTable\\n\\t{mso-style-name:\\\"Table Normal\\\";\\n\\tmso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\\n\\tmso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\\n\\tmso-style-noshow:yes;\\n\\tmso-style-priority:99;\\n\\tmso-style-parent:\\\"\\\";\\n\\tmso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\\n\\tmso-para-margin-top:0in;\\n\\tmso-para-margin-right:0in;\\n\\tmso-para-margin-bottom:8.0pt;\\n\\tmso-para-margin-left:0in;\\n\\tline-height:107%;\\n\\tmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\\n\\tfont-size:11.0pt;\\n\\tfont-family:\\\"Calibri\\\",sans-serif;\\n\\tmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\\n\\tmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\\n\\tmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\\n\\tmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\\n\\tmso-bidi-font-family:\\\"Times New Roman\\\";\\n\\tmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\\n<\\/style>\\n<![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\\n <o:shapedefaults v:ext=\\\"edit\\\" spidmax=\\\"1026\\\"\\/>\\n<\\/xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\\n <o:shapelayout v:ext=\\\"edit\\\">\\n  <o:idmap v:ext=\\\"edit\\\" data=\\\"1\\\"\\/>\\n <\\/o:shapelayout><\\/xml><![endif]-->\\n<\\/head>\\n\\n<body lang=EN-US style=\'tab-interval:.5in\'>\\n\\n<div class=WordSection1>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Big Brothers\\nBig Sisters recognizes that online social media (Facebook, <span class=SpellE>MySpace<\\/span>,\\nTwitter, LinkedIn, Blogs, <span class=SpellE>etc<\\/span>) has become a very\\npopular communications tool and that many of our Big Brothers\\/Sisters and\\nLittle Brothers\\/Sisters use these websites.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0\\n<\\/span>In general, personal use of social media sites is typically for\\ncommunications between peers, including friends and family.<span\\nstyle=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>BBBS wants to reiterate that your\\nrelationship with your Little is that of a mentor and role model, in addition\\nto a friend.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>Not all social media sites\\nare designed to support mentoring relationships. <o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Please\\nproceed thoughtfully when inviting or accepting an invitation from your Little\\nor their parent to a social media site.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0\\n<\\/span>If you have any doubts, please contact your Match Support Specialist\\nand\\/or postpone your invitation or acceptance.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0\\n<\\/span>If you choose to participate in a social media site with your Little or\\ntheir parent, you must adhere to the following guidelines regarding any\\npostings related to your match or affiliation with BBBS:<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<ol style=\'margin-top:0in\' start=1 type=1>\\n <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\'><b\\n     style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\\n     line-height:107%\'>Child safety must be a top priority at all times.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n <ul style=\'margin-top:0in\' type=circle>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Do not participate in any\\n      online communication with\\/about your Little unless you have discussed\\n      this with the parent\\/guardian or Match Support Specialist and have received\\n      their approval.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Never post any pictures of your\\n      Little online unless you have written consent from the child\\u2019s\\n      parent\\/guardian.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>That consent form\\n      should be filed with BBBS.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Never post any identifying\\n      information about your Little, especially contact information (<span\\n      class=SpellE>ie<\\/span>: child\\u2019s home address, school the child attends,\\n      where the parent works, etc.).<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>If you allow your Little to\\n      have access to the internet or social media during your match activity,\\n      you are responsible for monitoring the usage and assuring that your\\n      Little is on appropriate sites.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n <\\/ul>\\n <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\'><b\\n     style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\\n     line-height:107%\'>You are responsible for acting as a role model at all\\n     times.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n <ul style=\'margin-top:0in\' type=circle>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Use sound judgment with your\\n      communication, as you are a representing Big Brothers Big Sisters of\\n      Central Iowa, even if the agency isn\\u2019t directly connected to the message.<b\\n      style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Never post anything that could\\n      be perceived as judgmental or offensive to your Little or his\\/her\\n      parent\\/guardian.<b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Be aware of other postings on\\n      your page that are not BBBS related or are inappropriate for minors. Know\\n      that as a BBBS volunteer you are a role model at all times. Please ensure\\n      that all contents are appropriate and kid-friendly, in case your Little\\n      or his\\/her family were to read your social media page. If the social\\n      media site allows, create a separate group for your Little, his\\/her\\n      parent\\/guardian and BBBS staff that limits your Little\\u2019s access to your\\n      general or universal postings.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n <\\/ul>\\n<\\/ol>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'margin-left:1.0in;mso-add-space:auto\'><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<ol style=\'margin-top:0in\' start=3 type=1>\\n <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\'><b\\n     style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\\n     line-height:107%\'>Parent\\/Guardian permission is required.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n <ul style=\'margin-top:0in\' type=circle>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Give the parent\\/guardian and\\n      BBBS your website address, and when possible link your page to the BBBS page\\n      on that site so that we can follow along with your postings. We are\\n      active on Facebook, Twitter and our blog.<b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:\\n      normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Make sure that your page\\n      settings are set to private, so that only people you approve can view\\n      your online content. Ensure that BBBS and the parent\\/guardian are\\n      approved if you plan to post content related to your match.<b\\n      style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n <\\/ul>\\n <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\'><b\\n     style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\\n     line-height:107%\'>Confidentiality must be maintained at all times.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n <ul style=\'margin-top:0in\' type=circle>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Do not post the last name of a\\n      Little or their family, including but not limited to tagging them in a\\n      post or photo.<b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Honor confidentiality\\n      guidelines within your match: be cautious when posting detailed\\n      information about conversations with your Little, their parent\\/guardian,\\n      or with BBBS staff.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>Posting\\n      generalized information or status updates is typically appropriate, but\\n      lengthier postings or blogs containing in-depth information should be\\n      approved by the parent\\/guardian and by BBBS prior to posting.<b\\n      style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\'><span\\n      style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Do not post information that\\n      can only be assessed through Big Deals, Match Activities emails or\\n      through BBBS newsletters. The opportunities posted on Big Deals and Match\\n      Activities are intended for current <span class=SpellE>Bigs<\\/span> only,\\n      not the general public.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n <\\/ul>\\n <li class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\'><b\\n     style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\\n     line-height:107%\'>When in doubt about whether or not something is\\n     appropriate to post, consult with your Match Support Specialist prior to\\n     posting.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n<\\/ol>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>Failure to\\nadhere to these guidelines may result in the termination of your match.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%\'>I have read\\nand understand the social media guidelines set by Big Brothers Big Sisters of\\nCentral Iowa.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>By signing this document,\\nI pledge to abide by these guidelines.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=Mso