bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\\n<\\/style>\\n<![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\\n <o:shapedefaults v:ext=\\\"edit\\\" spidmax=\\\"1026\\\"\\/>\\n<\\/xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\\n <o:shapelayout v:ext=\\\"edit\\\">\\n  <o:idmap v:ext=\\\"edit\\\" data=\\\"1\\\"\\/>\\n <\\/o:shapelayout><\\/xml><![endif]-->\\n<\\/head>\\n\\n<body lang=EN-US style=\'tab-interval:.5in\'>\\n\\n<div class=WordSection1>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Big Brothers\\nBig Sisters recognizes that online social media (Facebook, MySpace, Twitter,\\nLinkedIn, Blogs, etc) has become a very popular communications tool and that\\nmany of our Big Brothers\\/Sisters and Little Brothers\\/Sisters use these\\nwebsites.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>In general, personal use of\\nsocial media sites is typically for communications between peers, including\\nfriends and family.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>BBBS wants to\\nreiterate that your relationship with your Little is that of a mentor and role\\nmodel, in addition to a friend.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>Not all\\nsocial media sites are designed to support mentoring relationships. <o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Please\\nproceed thoughtfully when inviting or accepting an invitation from your Little\\nor their parent to a social media site.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0\\n<\\/span>If you have any doubts, please contact your Match Support Specialist\\nand\\/or postpone your invitation or acceptance.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0\\n<\\/span>If you choose to participate in a social media site with your Little or\\ntheir parent, you must adhere to the following guidelines regarding any\\npostings related to your match or affiliation with BBBS:<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<ol style=\'margin-top:0in\' start=1 type=1>\\n <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\'><b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:\\n     normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Child safety must\\n     be a top priority at all times.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n <ul style=\'margin-top:0in\' type=circle>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Do not participate in any online communication\\n      with\\/about your Little unless you have discussed this with the\\n      parent\\/guardian or Match Support Specialist and have received their\\n      approval.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Never post any pictures of your Little online\\n      unless you have written consent from the child\\u2019s parent\\/guardian.<span\\n      style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>That consent form should be filed with\\n      BBBS.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Never post any identifying information about\\n      your Little, especially contact information (ie: child\\u2019s home address,\\n      school the child attends, where the parent works, etc.).<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>If you allow your Little to have access to the\\n      internet or social media during your match activity, you are responsible\\n      for monitoring the usage and assuring that your Little is on appropriate\\n      sites.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n <\\/ul>\\n <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\'><b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:\\n     normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>You are\\n     responsible for acting as a role model at all times.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n <ul style=\'margin-top:0in\' type=circle>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Use sound judgment with your communication, as\\n      you are a representing Big Brothers Big Sisters of Central Iowa, even if\\n      the agency isn\\u2019t directly connected to the message.<b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:\\n      normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Never post anything that could be perceived as\\n      judgmental or offensive to your Little or his\\/her parent\\/guardian.<b\\n      style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Be aware of other postings on your page that are\\n      not BBBS related or are inappropriate for minors. Know that as a BBBS\\n      volunteer you are a role model at all times. Please ensure that all\\n      contents are appropriate and kid-friendly, in case your Little or his\\/her\\n      family were to read your social media page. If the social media site\\n      allows, create a separate group for your Little, his\\/her parent\\/guardian\\n      and BBBS staff that limits your Little\\u2019s access to your general or\\n      universal postings.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n <\\/ul>\\n<\\/ol>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormalCxSpMiddle style=\'margin-left:1.0in;mso-add-space:auto\'><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<ol style=\'margin-top:0in\' start=3 type=1>\\n <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\'><b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:\\n     normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Parent\\/Guardian\\n     permission is required.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n <ul style=\'margin-top:0in\' type=circle>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Give the parent\\/guardian and BBBS your website\\n      address, and when possible link your page to the BBBS page on that site\\n      so that we can follow along with your postings. We are active on\\n      Facebook, Twitter and our blog.<b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Make sure that your page settings are set to\\n      private, so that only people you approve can view your online content.\\n      Ensure that BBBS and the parent\\/guardian are approved if you plan to post\\n      content related to your match.<b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n <\\/ul>\\n <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\'><b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:\\n     normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Confidentiality\\n     must be maintained at all times.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n <ul style=\'margin-top:0in\' type=circle>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Do not post the last name of a Little or their family,\\n      including but not limited to tagging them in a post or photo.<b\\n      style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Honor confidentiality guidelines within your\\n      match: be cautious when posting detailed information about conversations\\n      with your Little, their parent\\/guardian, or with BBBS staff.<span\\n      style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\u00a0 <\\/span>Posting generalized information or\\n      status updates is typically appropriate, but lengthier postings or blogs\\n      containing in-depth information should be approved by the parent\\/guardian\\n      and by BBBS prior to posting.<b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/b><\\/span><\\/li>\\n  <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level2 lfo3\'><span style=\'font-size:\\n      12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Do not post information that can only be\\n      assessed through Big Deals, Match Activities emails or through BBBS\\n      newsletters. The opportunities posted on Big Deals and Match Activities\\n      are intended for current Bigs only, not the general public.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/li>\\n <\\/ul>\\n <li class=MsoNormal style=\'mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\'><b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:\\n     normal\'><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>When in doubt\\n     about whether or not something is appropriate to post, consult with your\\n     Match Support Specialist prior to posting.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/b><\\/li>\\n<\\/ol>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:106%\'>Failure to\\nadhere to these guidelines may result in the termination of your match.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<\\/div>\\n\\n<\\/body>\\n\\n<\\/html>\\n\",\"productField\":\"\",\"multipleFiles\":false,\"maxFiles\":\"\",\"calculationFormula\":\"\",\"calculationRounding\":\"\",\"enableCalculation\":\"\",\"disableQuantity\":false,\"displayAllCategories\":false,\"useRichTextEditor\":false,\"pageNumber\":1,\"fields\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"captcha\",\"id\":2,\"label\":\"CAPTCHA\",\"adminLabel\":\"\",\"isRequired\":false,\"size\":\"medium\",\"errorMessage\":\"\",\"visibility\":\"visible\",\"inputs\":null,\"displayOnly\":true,\"formId\":9,\"description\":\"\",\"allowsPrepopulate\":false,\"inputMask\":false,\"inputMaskValue\":\"\",\"inputMaskIsCustom\":\"\",\"maxLength\":\"\",\"inputType\":\"\",\"labelPlacement\":\"\",\"descriptionPlacement\":\"\",\"subLabelPlacement\"