-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\\n\\\"Times New Roman\\\"\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style=\'font-family:\\\"Arial\\\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\\n\\\"Times New Roman\\\"\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<br style=\'mso-ignore:vglayout\' clear=ALL>\\n\\n<p class=MsoBodyText><span style=\'font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal\'>Volunteer\\ufffds\\nName: <u><span style=\'mso-tab-count:3\'>\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd <\\/span><span\\nstyle=\'mso-tab-count:2\'>\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd <\\/span><span style=\'mso-tab-count:\\n2\'>\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd <\\/span><span style=\'mso-tab-count:3\'>\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd <\\/span><span\\nstyle=\'mso-tab-count:2\'>\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd <\\/span><\\/u><\\/span><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-weight:normal\'><span\\nstyle=\'mso-tab-count:2\'>\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd\\ufffd <\\/span><span\\nstyle=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\ufffd<\\/span><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoBodyText style=\'margin-left:.4in\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoBodyText style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>Big\\nBrothers Big Sisters is a program designed to help children who have a defined\\nneed for a strong relationship with an interested adult.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.4in;text-align:justify\'><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:\\nnormal\'><span style=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>\\ufffd<span style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\'>Big\\nBrothers Big Sisters of Central Iowa impacts youth by empowering them to\\ndiscover and achieve their goals through meaningful mentoring relationships.\\ufffd<\\/span><\\/span><\\/b><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'> \\ufffd Mission Statement<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><span\\nstyle=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\ufffd<\\/span><o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>The\\nevaluation interviews are designed to establish a profile of your capacities in\\nrelating to children and your interests. Except for parents and\\/or guardians\\nwith a direct responsibility for a Little Brother\\/Sister who has been\\nevaluated, approved for a match, and is actively being considered for a match\\nwith you, the information you provide the agency will be handled in a\\nconfidential manner.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.4in;text-align:justify\'><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoBodyTextIndent style=\'margin-left:0in;text-align:justify\'><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\\\"Times New Roman\\\",serif\'>The desires of a\\nchild\\ufffds parent or guardian and the wishes of the Big Brother or Big Sister are\\nrespected in the selection of the appropriate adult and child to be matched.\\nRelevant information will be provided to each party in a prospective match\\nregarding the other, but names will be withheld until the parties agree to\\nenter into a pre-match discussion. Relevant information shall include past or\\npresent factors of health, personality, behavior of each individual and\\/or\\nfamily that your Case Manager determines may have a significant effect on the\\nrelationship. Any party has the right to refuse to enter into the match based\\nupon the information communicated. <o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoBodyText style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>Big\\nBrothers Big Sister of <st1:place w:st=\\\"on\\\">Central Iowa<\\/st1:place> maintains\\nsupervision after the match is made. During the supervision of the match, your\\nCase Manager will share relevant information that, in their opinion, will be\\nnecessary to help the relationship depend and\\/or resolve problems.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoBodyText style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:11.0pt;\\nfont-weight:normal\'>All parties in the match, including staff members of Big\\nBrothers Big Sisters, will handle information in a confidential and appropriate\\nmanner.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.4in;text-align:justify\'><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.4in;text-align:justify\'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:line\\n id=\\\"_x0000_s1039\\\" style=\'position:absolute;left:0;text-align:left;z-index:251657728\'\\n from=\\\"-9pt,3.4pt\\\" to=\\\"513pt,3.4pt\\\"\\/><![endif]--><![if !vml]><span\\nstyle=\'mso-ignore:vglayout;position:relative;z-index:251657728;left:-13px;\\ntop:4px;width:698px;height:6px\'><img width=698 height=2\\nsrc=\\\"EXHIBIT%20D.1%20-%20Volunteer%20Agreement-2018_files\\/image004.gif\\\" v:shapes=\\\"_x0000_s1039\\\"><\\/span><![endif]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<br style=\'mso-ignore:vglayout\' clear=ALL>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'text-align:justify\'><span style=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>If\\n<u>applicable<\\/u> and as an agency volunteer:<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.4in;text-align:justify\'><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><o:p>&nbsp;<\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in\'><![if !supportLists]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>1)<span\\nstyle=\'font:7.0pt \\\"Times New Roman\\\"\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><![endif]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>I agree that, upon notification, I will adhere to all\\nnew policies and procedures adopted by Big Brothers Big Sisters of Central\\nIowa.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in\'><![if !supportLists]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>2)<span\\nstyle=\'font:7.0pt \\\"Times New Roman\\\"\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><![endif]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>I understand that overnight visits are <b\\nstyle=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><u>NOT<\\/u><\\/b> allowed except in rare\\ncircumstances and only after prior approval has been given by the agency.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in\'><![if !supportLists]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size: