that the approved volunteer(s) is\\/are the\\nonly one(s) authorized, under the BBBS agency insurance policy to transport the\\nlittle.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in\'><![if !supportLists]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>7)<span\\nstyle=\'font:7.0pt \\\"Times New Roman\\\"\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><![endif]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>I agree to spend time with my LB\\/LS <i>primarily<\\/i>\\non a one-to-one basis.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\ufffd <\\/span>A guest or other\\nfamily member should only be included if both parties agree and are present\\nthroughout the duration of the outing.<span style=\'mso-spacerun:yes\'>\\ufffd\\n<\\/span>No volunteer to ever be alone with their Little\\ufffds guest or other family\\nmember.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in\'><![if !supportLists]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>8)<span\\nstyle=\'font:7.0pt \\\"Times New Roman\\\"\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><![endif]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>I agree to be a consistent Brother\\/Sister role model;\\none the child can depend on and trust in.<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=MsoNormal style=\'margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list .5in\'><![if !supportLists]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'><span style=\'mso-list:Ignore\'>9)<span\\nstyle=\'font:7.0pt \\\"Times New Roman\\\"\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><![endif]><span\\nstyle=\'font-size:11.0pt\'>I agree to keep my Case Manager informed about the\\nprogress in my match by contacting him\\/her monthly during the first year 